1
00:00:03,861 --> 00:00:07,971
You tell me what is happiness
in Kṛṣṇa consciousness;

2
00:00:09,887 --> 00:00:13,750
all happiness—
beginning, middle, and end.

3
00:00:14,440 --> 00:00:17,568
[Spiritual Capitalism]

4
00:00:17,711 --> 00:00:21,588
But I remember, once, 
in Śrīla Prabhupād’s garden in Los Angeles,

5
00:00:21,588 --> 00:00:23,318
he was giving this sequence:

6
00:00:23,318 --> 00:00:26,928
ādau-śraddhā, sādhu-saṅga,
bhajana-kriyā,

7
00:00:26,945 --> 00:00:30,482
and talking about that,
and telling each stage.

8
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:35,901
But when he got to bhāva,
and then when he came to prema,

9
00:00:36,249 --> 00:00:40,228
he said, “Then: enjoyment.”

10
00:00:43,252 --> 00:00:44,505
But Guru Mahārāj
again would say,

11
00:00:44,505 --> 00:00:46,393
“But what is that enjoyment?”

12
00:00:46,393 --> 00:00:50,121
“‘Dasa' kari' vetana more
deha prema-dhana” (Cc: 3.20.37):

13
00:00:50,962 --> 00:00:53,945
what they call
‘compound interest’.

14
00:00:54,335 --> 00:00:57,728
Are there any economists
in the group?

15
00:00:57,728 --> 00:01:00,310
No, you’re a bunch of Marxists.

16
00:01:00,310 --> 00:01:02,445
[Laughs]

17
00:01:02,445 --> 00:01:06,504
Compound interest, 
only a capitalist can understand this:

18
00:01:06,683 --> 00:01:11,509
they invest their capital,
then the interest comes,

19
00:01:11,826 --> 00:01:13,788
what do you do 
with the interest?

20
00:01:13,788 --> 00:01:16,115
People go, “Well we’ll go buy something,
spend it!”

21
00:01:16,730 --> 00:01:19,053
Not a real capitalist.
Real capitalists know:

22
00:01:19,053 --> 00:01:22,718
I got some interest?
Increase the capital.

23
00:01:23,004 --> 00:01:25,620
Now the capital’s greater,
more interest will come:

24
00:01:25,620 --> 00:01:27,450
increase the capital.

25
00:01:27,906 --> 00:01:30,810
Guru Mahārāj said that the devotees
are like that. They’re serving,

26
00:01:30,810 --> 00:01:35,241
then, when the time comes:
increase the serving capital.

27
00:01:35,241 --> 00:01:38,087
More interest?
Increase the service capital.

28
00:01:39,338 --> 00:01:44,029
So real prema, real enjoyment,
is sevā.

29
00:01:47,826 --> 00:01:49,441
Hare Kṛṣṇa.

